<!--page/oneself/pages/Instructions/Instructions.wxml-->
<view class="top">
  <view class="ToUse" bindtap='ToUse'>
    <image src="https://image.yuelvhui.com/pubfile/2019/09/23/line_1569232830_24058.png"></image>
    <text>邀请好友</text>
  </view>
  <view class="Total">
    <view class="item">
      <view>总计次数</view>
      <view class="num">{{sale.total}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="s"></view>
    <view class="item">
      <view>已用次数</view>
      <view class="num">{{sale.use}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="s"></view>
    <view class="item">
      <view>剩余次数</view>
      <view class="num">{{sale.unUse}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="con">
  <view class="GetInstructions">
    <view class="title">
      获取途径
    </view>
    <view class="content">
      推荐的用户，线上支付399元成为会员后，可增加一次立减50元优惠次数。
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="GetInstructions">
    <view class="title">
      使用说明
    </view>
    <view class="content">
      <view>1. 客房满150元/间夜，所有房型可用</view>
      <view>2. 每单仅限使用一次立减50元优惠（系统自动减免）</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="case">
    <view class="tit">
      案例说明
    </view>
    <view class="caseContent">
      <view class="item">
        <view class="casetitle">1.如帐号有直推立减50元优惠次数，则预定酒店时默认使用</view>
        <image src="/images/personalCenter/rule1.png" style="height:390rpx;"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="item">
        <view class="casetitle">2.立减50元优惠明细</view>
        <image src="/images/personalCenter/rule2.png" style="height:336rpx"></image>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>